Class ScheduleElementImpl

java.lang.Object
  org.cougaar.planning.ldm.plan.ScheduleElementImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:

Direct Known Subclasses:
AssignedAvailabilityElementImpl, AssignedRelationshipElementImpl, LocationRangeScheduleElementImpl, LocationScheduleElementImpl, RelationshipImpl
public class ScheduleElementImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements ScheduleElement, NewScheduleElement, java.io.Serializable

Base class for ScheduleElement. Millisecond accuracy times are stored in seconds since java epoch start, GMT. Start time is closed, end time is open.
